    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Members of a family containing about 12 species of Old World birds with stocky legs, colorful blue and violet patches, and called "rollers" for the dives and somersaults they perform during courtship.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
